  <div class="detail-grid">
    <div class="detail-section full ab">
      <div class="slabel">◎ Overview</div>
      <p class="stext" style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.9;">A multi-node industrial sensor platform implementing Modbus-RTU over RS-485 to poll an NPK (Nitrogen, Phosphorus, Potassium) soil sensor and stream calibrated live readings to an LCD display. Led as team lead, achieving 88.9% validated measurement accuracy against certified soil references.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:2px;" class="detail-grid">
    <div class="detail-section ab2">
      <div class="slabel">⊙ System Objective</div>
      <p class="stext">Design and implement a real-time soil nutrient monitoring system capable of querying an industrial NPK sensor over a multi-node RS-485 bus using the Modbus-RTU protocol, calibrate raw register values to engineering units, and display live readings on an LCD.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-section">
      <div class="slabel">⊘ Design Constraints</div>
      <div class="spec-list"><div class="spec-item">RS-485 bus must support multi-node topology; firmware must handle bus arbitration and direction switching</div><div class="spec-item">Modbus-RTU register map must exactly match sensor vendor specification; off-by-one addressing causes total read failure</div><div class="spec-item">ADC scaling must convert raw 16-bit register values to calibrated ppm readings via vendor-provided voltage decode equations</div><div class="spec-item">LCD update latency must not block the polling cycle; display writes must be non-blocking</div><div class="spec-item">System must achieve ≥85% accuracy against certified soil reference standards</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:2px;">
    <div class="detail-section full">
      <div class="slabel">⊞ System Architecture</div>
      <div class="arch-diagram">┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              SOIL SENSOR SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE          │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                       │
│   <span class="ah">[Arduino Mega]</span>  ──UART<span class="ah2">──►</span>  <span class="ah">[RS-485 Transceiver]</span>    │
│         │                         │                  │
│    Firmware (C)             RS-485 Bus (Half-Duplex)  │
│    ├─ Modbus-RTU                   │                  │
│    ├─ CRC-16 Engine          <span class="ah">[NPK Sensor Node]</span>        │
│    ├─ Register Map           Modbus Slave ID: 0x01    │
│    └─ LCD Driver                   │                  │
│         │                   Register 0x1E – N (ppm)  │
│   <span class="ah">[16x2 LCD]</span>                Register 0x1F – P (ppm)  │
